docs/source/domain-model.md:242:### Active Member Rule for Individuals
docs/source/domain-model.md:246:1. Avail services offered by SFPCL directly or indirectly, such as crop production, procurement, purchase or sale of agricultural inputs.
docs/source/domain-model.md:247:2. Supply primary produce for a continuous period of four financial years to SFPCL, subsidiaries, step-down subsidiaries or through a Producer Institution member supplying to these entities.
docs/source/domain-model.md:256:## 7.3 ProducerInstitutionProfile
docs/source/domain-model.md:271:### Active Member Rule for Producer Institutions
docs/source/domain-model.md:275:1. Be a member of SFPCL.
docs/source/domain-model.md:276:2. Avail services offered by SFPCL directly or indirectly.
docs/source/domain-model.md:277:3. Supply primary produce continuously for four financial years to SFPCL, subsidiaries or step-down subsidiaries.
