docs/source/domain-model.md:581:### Eligibility Conditions
docs/source/domain-model.md:583:1. Applicant must be active member of the FPC / company.
docs/source/domain-model.md:584:2. Applicant should not be in default for any FPC loan of SFPCL or subsidiary / associate company.
docs/source/domain-model.md:585:3. Applicant must submit land documents, KYC, bank statement and crop plan.
docs/source/domain-model.md:586:4. Applicant must agree to loan sanction terms as per Term Sheet and Loan Agreement.
docs/source/domain-model.md:587:5. Loan purpose must be crop production or agriculture activity only.
