docs/source/auth-permissions.md:232:## 6.3 Logout Flow
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:247:## 6.4 Password Reset Flow
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:249:1. User requests reset.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:250:2. System sends secure reset link / OTP to registered email.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:251:3. User sets new password.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:252:4. All active refresh tokens are revoked.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:253:5. Audit log is created.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:255:## 6.5 Sensitive Action Re-Authentication Flow
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:259:1. User clicks sensitive action.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:260:2. Backend checks whether recent authentication is still valid.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:261:3. If not, frontend prompts for password or OTP.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:262:4. Backend issues short-lived sensitive-action confirmation.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:263:5. User completes action.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:264:6. Audit log records re-authentication and action.
