docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2735:1. JWT authentication for all API access.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2736:2. Role-based permissions for module actions.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2737:3. Team and assignment scope for operational queues.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2738:4. Object-level access for applications, loans, documents and approvals.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2739:5. Workflow-state guards for every state transition.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2740:6. Approval-authority validation for sanction, exception, disbursement and recovery.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2741:7. Conflict-of-interest checks for director / relative cases.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2742:8. Maker-checker enforcement for appraisal, approval, documentation and disbursement.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2743:9. Sensitive data masking and audited reveal workflows.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2744:10. Restricted document access with download audit.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2745:11. Immutable audit logs for all critical actions.
docs/source/auth-permissions.md:2746:12. Explicit backend enforcement independent of frontend visibility.
